<div id="review_3671429396" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3671429396" />
    <a title="Cooper Ackerly" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/103383457-cooper-ackerly"><img alt="Cooper Ackerly" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1621955127p2/103383457.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3671429396?book_show_action=true">Nov 30, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cooper Ackerly" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cooper Ackerly" href="/user/show/103383457-cooper-ackerly">Cooper Ackerly</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/19228131-historia-calamitatum">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3671429396" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13972990261091273191">Having exercised more self-control than Abelard apparently did in his entire life by not making lewd comments about the whole Abelard-and-Heloise thing, I can only observe that Abelard was insufferable, smarter than everyone in the room and knew it, gifted with an invective that would have made him a wonderful literary critic, and redeemed from his gross sexism only by the fact that he fell in love with Heloise, who was obviously more awesome than he was. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


