<span id="freeTextContainer14754602962269991557">I actually read this book online through Project Gutenberg. It is a memoir telling the story of Abelard&apos;s life and adventures, with particular focus on his epic romance. But, of course, this is a story which took place during the 12th century AD, adding an interesting layer of historical interest to what otherwise reads as a rather modern tale.</span>
  <span id="freeText14754602962269991557" style="display:none">I actually read this book online through Project Gutenberg. It is a memoir telling the story of Abelard's life and adventures, with particular focus on his epic romance. But, of course, this is a story which took place during the 12th century AD, adding an interesting layer of historical interest to what otherwise reads as a rather modern tale.</span>
