<span id="freeTextContainer13255616573153660771">Too much whining and griping; not enough theological reflection on suffering from a supposedly brilliant mind. He&apos;s just an arrogant prick, a case study in what theologians hope not to become.</span>
  <span id="freeText13255616573153660771" style="display:none">Too much whining and griping; not enough theological reflection on suffering from a supposedly brilliant mind. He's just an arrogant prick, a case study in what theologians hope not to become.</span>
